body.description: The Pyle In-Wall/Ceiling Speakers deliver stereo sound to any room in your home or office. Each speaker comes equipped with a high compliance polymer tweeter delivering a full, rich sound without cluttering floor space. Speakers are made of nature friendly ABS material and include changeable round and square grills. The system features spring-loaded speaker terminals for quick connection and comes with a cut-out template for easy installation. Mount them in a convenient location on the wall or ceiling for a flush, clean look. Achieve wide-range sound performance and add audio to any room with the Pyle In-Wall/Ceiling Speakers. reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 18, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great bang for your buck
reviews.reviewText: I installed these in our small 3 man office, and now we get to enjoy some tunes while we work. They sound great for the price and we're painless to install (they included a cutting guide which removed the guesswork from cutting the ceiling tiles). 5/5

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewText: They work great in my bathroom.Sound is awesome!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 24, 2023
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Works great so far, wanted to add speakers upstairs so we didn't have to crank the basement and she the house to hear everything upstairs. Install was simple, minus attic insulation haha. They are 16 ohm so volume is not as loud as the other system speakers but not a major difference. I paired them with the Pyle for channel selector and I am not disappointed. Only time will tell on actually quality but everything seems well made. Need to get some outdoor speakers for the patio and garage now and will most likely go with Pyle again

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great deal for solid ceiling speakers
reviews.reviewText: Great speakers for the price. I am using them as surround speakers installed in my drop ceiling. Sound quality is really nice for the average user. 200 watt delivers nice power. Easy to install. Be aware these are 16 ohms so you need a suitable amp/reciever. Bottom line- if you are looking for basic cheap in ceiling speakers, look no further.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Surprising sound for price point
reviews.reviewText: First off, these speakers are not the best speakers you’ll ever hear. But in-ceiling speakers don’t need to be! These speakers are perfect for whole home audio and work great and sound quite respectable, especially considering their price point. I have gotten worse sound from speakers 2x the cost. They are a little lacking in the bass department, but you can EQ them to sound pretty good. All in all, very happy, 5 stars.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 17, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I have had great success with Pyle speackers bought 6 more. Very easy installation and sound great.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good pair of analog speakers to install in-ceiling along with the Pyle Receiver
reviews.reviewText: In a digital world with lot of processing that are embedded in DAC, it's better to use this pair of speakers with pure analog world with a Pyle receiver. The fidelity of the sound coming from these speakers is amazing.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 18, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Replacement Speakers - Work Great
reviews.reviewText: I bought this brand when I moved into my home 7 years ago. One of my speakers started to separate from the ceiling and turns out the plastic ring was disintegrating - fell apart like brittle when I removed it from the ceiling. Bought these to replace the old ones. They did not disappoint - the ring of these new ones feels like a hard plastic or even metal. And hey - for 7 years, that one speaker worked perfectly. And for the record, the other 7 speakers I installed 7 years ago are still working just fine.Great brand for the value. And sound is excellent for my home theater, bedroom and dining room.

reviews.reviewTitle: Great speakers for my surround sound
reviews.reviewText: I tested the speakers before cutting my ceiling open and installing. For the price, these speakers have a warm bass sound and the highs are nice as well. The sound out of these drivers are nice and clear. I created a compass out of a wood shim and drywall screw and nail. Stud finder to find the joists and cut the circle in the middle.Now wired for 7.2 sound, movies are much more immersive with this pair of speakers added.Great product from a name brand known for quality speakers. Very happy with my purchase.Thanks so much Pyle!!!
good product beware of Fastway deliveries .

reviews.reviewTitle: Mal producto, mal servicio de Amazon
reviews.reviewText: Estas bocinas vienen descritas como Bluetooth, pero no especifican que se necesita comprar un amplificador aparte. Además que el servicio de Amazon devoluciones es una estafa, me estimaron una devolución de 2500 pesos y resulta que solo me regresaron 76 pesos, ahora no tengo producto ni dinero y no sé a dónde contactar para hacer un reclamo
